{"tid":2022691,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[TW] 想問各位巴絲打有關各類工程學科出路and前景?","createTime":"2020-05-18T12:49:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-19T15:59:02.000Z","uid":196621,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"4a7157d0cff2cd78e6a7b461ed85cb8198b2b305","tid":2022691,"uid":196621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T12:49:36.000Z","msg":"話說小弟打算去<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">TW</span></span>讀工程,但發現工程學分好多大科:<br />\n電機,土木,機械,化工,材料,數學,物理,生物化學&hellip;..<br />\n睇到好亂 (大概知要讀D咩)<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n想問下各位巴絲打知吾知,邊個大科出路廣D(易搵工)/ 邊個領域最爭人手<br />\n<br />\n同埋之前睇到有D其他web有得考牌<br />\nEg: <a href=\"http://www.csme.org.tw/Default.aspx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.csme.org.tw%2FDefault.aspx&d=pzZXWUTiTgu0UE2nVnCkChPX6nNrjY8iteK6A9FjwF0%3D&h=f8364ba2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.csme.org.tw/Default.aspx</a><br />\n除左大學grad之外有冇野<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">MUST</span></span>要去考or要特別去學<br />\n<br />\n(p.s.本身睇完打算入機械工程,如果有香港工程人不妨分享下)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d87575bf8337cf03c94dd463a710277b509652de","tid":2022691,"uid":15516,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T12:52:13.000Z","msg":"工程悔終生 <br />\n頭痛住答你"},{"pid":"68f8ba4cef6c26b939f18f1fc5f2f7d4bbe6e727","tid":2022691,"uid":196621,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"d87575bf8337cf03c94dd463a710277b509652de","tid":2022691,"uid":15516,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T12:52:13.000Z","msg":"工程悔終生 <br />\n頭痛住答你"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T12:58:00.000Z","msg":"有冇咁差呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />      <br />\nching本身讀咩?做緊工程?<br />\n人工好差?定讀完0用途?定其